'''J.J. Schaffer''' is the son of [[Leanne Schaffer]].

==History==
J.J. was at the hospital with his mother, Leanne, who was waiting for a heart transplant. When Shannon Iverson came in, they waited to see if her husband would agree to let her organs be donated, including her heart to Leanne. Her husband ultimately decided to donate her organs and her heart was given to Leanne.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
Because of her illness, J.J. and his brother, Mike, were helping to take care of their mother.

==Notes and Trivia==
*According to his brother, he's going to be a nurse.
